      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="mb-10" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-warm-black mb-4">What is AI-native search?</h2>
          <p class="text-warm-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            <strong>AI-native search</strong> is a search paradigm that understands natural language queries instead of matching keywords. When a user types "मलाई laptop को warranty बारेमा जानकारी चाहिन्छ" (I need information about laptop warranty), AI-native search understands the intent and returns the warranty policy directly—not a list of pages containing "laptop" and "warranty."
          </p>
          <p class="text-warm-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
            For Nepal, this matters because users naturally mix Nepali and English (code-switching), and traditional keyword search fails completely with these queries. AI-native search handles "best mobile phone 20,000 samma" as naturally as it handles pure English queries.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-10" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-warm-black mb-4">Why Nepal needs AI-native search</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600">
              <p class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-1">Code-switching is natural</p>
              <p class="text-warm-600">Nepali users routinely mix languages: "yo product को delivery charge kati ho?" Keyword search can't handle this. AI search can.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600">
              <p class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-1">Leapfrog legacy technology</p>
              <p class="text-warm-600">Many Nepali businesses haven't invested heavily in search. This is an opportunity to skip keyword search entirely and go directly to AI-native.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600">
              <p class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-1">Competitive advantage</p>
              <p class="text-warm-600">Zero Nepali e-commerce sites offer AI-native search today. Early adopters will stand out immediately.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

